{% # Embed block v1.1.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v1.1.0 — top-margin override range widened to `-200…200` (was `0…200`): negative values pull a block tighter than the section rhythm. Pairs with `utility--block-layout-vars` v1.2.0 (emit on `!= 0`). See `.context/docs/schema-conventions.md` § Top-spacing pair.
  - v1.0.0 — initial
{% endcomment %}

